.TH man 1 "2 April 2022" "1.1" "vedit man page"
.SH NAME
    vedit - video editor
.SH SYNOPSIS
    vedit.sh [optional_input_file]
.SH DESCRIPTION
    video editor made for Systemy Operacyjne using ffmpeg as a basis and zenity for 
    script comes with 7 options:
    1: "Przycięcie" lets you choose when the video will start and end
    2: "Wstawianie" lets you join two or more videos into one  
    3: "Wstawianie ścieżki dzwiękowej" lets you add audio track to your 
    4: "czarno-biały filtr" makes video black and white
    5: "Podgląd aktualnego pliku" lets you preview changes made
    6: "Cofnij ostatnią zmianę" undos last change made
    7: "Export" exports video
.SH EXAMPLES
    vedit will open zenity file window.
    vedit example.mp4 will skip file window and open example.mp4 to edit.
.SH OPTIONS
    vedit does not take any options
.SH BUGS
    no known bugs.
.SH AUTHOR
   Krzysztof Napiórkowski ( s191689@student.pg.edu.pl )
.SH REPORTING BUGS
